^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|On the auction 1 minor-1@H-?, there is only 1 unbid major (spades). But there are 2 bids available to show spades, a negative double and 1@S. So experts differentiate between the meanings of the 2 bids. A negative double shows exactly 4 spades. And a bid of 1S shows 5 or more spades.|mb|1H|
